Package com.hyperwallet.android.model.graphql.field

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConditionalPattern
    ConditionalPattern represents the input field format regex pattern needed on creation of an account.
    DataType
    Input field data type, used to create input widget
    Field
    Field represents the account input field information needed on creation of an account.
    FieldGroup
    FieldGroup represents a logical grouping of fields
    FieldSelectionOption
    FieldSelectionOption represents selection option that a user can choose based on the required information from the input field
    FileSize
    FileSize representation
    Mask
    Mask represents input field information needed on Field Formatting.
    TransferMethodConfiguration
    Represents Users' program context Transfer Method Configuration information
    TransferMethodConfigurationField
    Represents Users' program context Transfer Method Configuration information with Fees
    TransferMethodConfigurationFieldResult
    TransferMethodConfigurationFieldResult implementation of HyperwalletTransferMethodConfigurationField
    ValidationMessage
    ValidationMessage represents validation error message data to be shown to user when one of the following errors are raised from user input: Length of input is not met Input pattern does not match If in case the input data is required, then input data should not be empty and will display empty message
